steps.step: {"blocks":[{"key":"7pls9","text":"Before starting protocol:","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"style":"bold","offset":0,"length":25}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"d8tbl","text":"1) pre-chill swinging bucket centrifuge and a fixed angle centrifuge to 4c","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"59rte","text":"2) Pre-chill dounces and pestles to 4c on ice","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"39k6c","text":"3) Pre-chill tubes","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"8rcfn","text":"4) Fill up 2 L beaker with 500 mL sterile water to soak the used Dounces","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

later","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"a7bvj","text":"7) Pellet nuclei by spinning 5 min at 4c at 350 xg in a fixed angle ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"7hhqo","text":"12) Layer 600 uL 40% Iodixanol solution under the 30% mixture. ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"5734u","text":"15) Take 200 uL of the nuclei band and put into 1.5 mL LoBind tube","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"37oh1","text":"16) Dilute nuclei by adding 200 uL of wash buffer and mix by pipetting","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"3h96","text":"17) Count nuclei using trypan blue","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"5rcsk","text":"18) Centrifuge at 500 xg for 5 min at 4c","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"b6gv7","text":"19) Remove supernatant without disrupting pellet","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"4kii3","text":"20) resuspend in x uL of chilled Nuclei Buffer (depending on what isolated nuclei are used for) to achieve target concentration based on count.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
